// BUG 4

Send To A Friend Does Not Email

// Description
The 'Send to a friend' button acts as if it will email a person information about the selected item, however no email is sent.

// How to Reproduce
Click the 'Send to a Friend' button, fill in the friend's name & email, click 'send'.

// Environment
Google Chrome browser version 96.0.4664.110 (64-bit)
Windows 10

// Expected Results
Users expect to have an email sent, especially since a confirmation box pops up notifying that an email was sent.

// Severity
High
